Nested Categories Extension
------------------------------------

Version: 2.1
Author: Andrey Lubinov (andrey.lubinov@gmail.com), Александр Бирюков (info@alexbirukov.ru)
Build Date: 03.10.2013


[INSTALLATION]

1. Upload the 'nestedcats' folder in this archive to your Symphony 'extensions' folder.
2. Enable it by selecting the "Nested Categories", choose Enable from the with-selected menu, then click Apply.


[USAGE]

1. Go to the Categories/Overview and add some categories.
2. Append "Nested Categories" field to your section.
3. Append "Nested Categories" Data Source to your page (optional).

- See Data Source's "about" section for example XML output and possible XSL template.

